description: Simply ask the Wacky Factory to tell you a fact from a hand-picked selection of some of the most interesting bits of knowledge available.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Wacky Factory to tell me a fact
Alexa, ask Wacky Factory to blow me away with a fact
Alexa, ask Wacky Factory to share a fact with me
name: Wacky Factory
shortDescription: Wacky Fact-ory: learn little-known facts that may seem hard to believe!
